         <bioghist encodinganalog="545">
            <p>Philip M. Wagner was the editor for Baltimore Sun and Baltimore Evening Sun; syndicated columnist; founder of Boordy Vineyard; author of books on viticulture and H.L. Mencken.</p>
         </bioghist>
         <arrangement encodinganalog="351">
            <p>Organized into three series: Series I. Personal, 1839-1994. Series II. Sun Papers, 1927-1995. Series III. Boordy Vineyard, 1933-1995.</p>
         </arrangement>
